title: Game of the Week: Green Valley defeats Coronado
text: Share Updated: 10/16 11:32 pm HENDERSON (KSNV News3LV) â€“ Green Valley rebounded from its loss in the Henderson Bowl to down Coronado 28-10 in the News 3 Operation Football Game of the Week.The Gators and Cougars had come off tough losses.In other scores around the Las Vegas Valley, Basic blanked Eldorado 52-0; Bishop Gorman downed Legacy 63-7; Desert Pines shut out Rancho 48-0; Las Vegas gets by Canyon Springs 34-22; Palo Verde pummeled Durango 47-0; Desert Oasis beat Cimarron-Memorial 49-7; Liberty smoked Valley 74-8; and Cheyenne defeated Western 58-0.
